title: June Hero Drop #1
body:
It's time for the new Heroes drop, two of them will be added to the Pool.

Voting for the next Heroes is open from 5/27/2021 till 5/30/2021!

Choose wisely! It depends only on you who will become the next heroes of the brutal battle in Crypto Kombat!
author: 0x6eFF8897098F418913341d606231f7Cbce1910Dd
